              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>C E Ferulic by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Defend against oxidative stress and brighten your complexion with this award-winning antioxidant serum.
                It helps support collagen production, smooths fine lines, and minimizes visible pores for firmer,
                healthier-looking skin.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Cell Cycle Catalyst</strong><br>
                Stimulate skin renewal and restore clarity with this advanced treatment. It refines pores, smooths rough
